metadata.name: Acanthus
metadata.description: Hand-drawn on Procreate. Black ink on tri-color background. 3300 px x 2550 px at 300 dpi. A skeleton fish that roams the depths of the Mad Sea. In the unknown depths that lie within us, heroes find the courage to meet their own sea monsters and discover who they truly are. But beware the jaws that bite and be mindful of the remnants of those who have foundered here. One of the OG characters of the Mad Sea Hieroglyphs Collection.
